# Set 029 Session 3 (per-session-set orchestrator marker, schema v3).
# The writer also drops a self-protecting `.gitignore` inside each
# `.dabbler/` directory so consumer repos that haven't patched their
# root `.gitignore` still avoid committing marker files; this entry
# is the workspace-root belt-and-suspenders.
docs/session-sets/*/.dabbler/
# Set 031 (delegation.decision_consensus V1). The per-decision
# JSONL journal (ai_router/consensus-decisions.jsonl) stays
# committed — same precedent as router-metrics.jsonl — so the
# audit trail survives across conversations. The disk-heavy
# full-payload sibling directory (Markdown, one file per call) is
# default-on and explicitly opt-outable via
# delegation.decision_consensus.journal_full_payloads_dir: null.
ai_router/consensus-decisions/
